<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('../partials/head') %>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Can BaZi predict if a relationship will work?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "BaZi compatibility analysis reveals the natural dynamic between two people — areas of harmony and potential friction. It doesn't predict success or failure, but highlights strengths to nurture and challenges to navigate. A clash doesn't doom a relationship, and a perfect match doesn't guarantee one."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What if our zodiac signs clash?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "A zodiac clash (such as Rat vs Horse) indicates areas of natural tension, but it's only one factor among many. Full BaZi compatibility examines all four pillars, element balance, and Day Master harmony. Many successful relationships have zodiac clashes offset by strong compatibility elsewhere in the chart."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Is BaZi compatibility the same as zodiac compatibility?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "No. Zodiac compatibility only considers the year animal, which is just one of eight characters in a BaZi chart. True BaZi compatibility analyzes both partners' complete Four Pillars — including Day Master, element balance, and all pillar interactions — for a far more nuanced and accurate assessment."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How important is birth time for compatibility?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Birth time determines the Hour Pillar, which represents inner emotions and private life — crucial for understanding romantic compatibility. Without birth time, you can still assess three of the four pillars, but the Hour Pillar adds significant depth to the analysis, especially for intimate relationships."
        }
      }
    ]
  }
  </script>
</head>
<body class="seo-page">
  <%- include('../partials/nav') %>

  <main class="seo-main">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="about-hero">
      <div class="about-hanzi">合</div>
      <h1 style="color:var(--text);font-size:26px;margin-bottom:10px;">BaZi Compatibility</h1>
      <p>Discover relationship harmony through Chinese astrology. Analyze zodiac clashes, element balance, and pillar interactions between two birth charts.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 1: What is BaZi Compatibility? -->
    <div class="about-section">
      <h3>What is BaZi Compatibility?</h3>
      <p>BaZi compatibility (<span style="font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;">合婚</span> <em>he hun</em>) is the traditional Chinese method of assessing relationship harmony between two people. Rooted in thousands of years of metaphysical practice, it was historically consulted before marriage arrangements to ensure a balanced union.</p>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:12px;margin:16px 0;">
        <div style="text-align:center;padding:16px 10px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border-radius:12px;">
          <div style="font-size:28px;margin-bottom:6px;">☯️</div>
          <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);">Element Balance</div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center;padding:16px 10px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border-radius:12px;">
          <div style="font-size:28px;margin-bottom:6px;">🏛️</div>
          <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);">Pillar Interactions</div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center;padding:16px 10px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border-radius:12px;">
          <div style="font-size:28px;margin-bottom:6px;">🐲</div>
          <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);">Zodiac Harmony</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>A full compatibility reading analyzes both partners' birth charts across all four pillars, comparing element strengths, identifying clashes and combinations, and determining whether the Day Masters support or challenge each other.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-callout">
      <strong>In Chinese tradition, compatibility readings were essential before marriage arrangements.</strong> Families would consult a BaZi master to ensure the union of two birth charts would produce harmony, prosperity, and healthy descendants.
    </div>

    <!-- Section 2: The Six Clashes -->
    <div class="about-section">
      <h3>The Six Clashes (<span style="font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;">六冲</span>)</h3>
      <p>The Six Clashes represent the strongest zodiac oppositions. When two animals sit directly across the zodiac wheel, their energies collide — creating friction, tension, and transformation.</p>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:12px;margin-top:16px;">
        <div style="background:rgba(220,60,60,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(220,60,60,0.18);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:6px;">🐀 ↔ 🐎</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text);font-weight:600;">Rat ↔ Horse</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;margin-top:2px;">子午冲</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:rgba(220,60,60,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(220,60,60,0.18);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:6px;">🐂 ↔ 🐑</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text);font-weight:600;">Ox ↔ Goat</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;margin-top:2px;">丑未冲</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:rgba(220,60,60,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(220,60,60,0.18);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:6px;">🐅 ↔ 🐒</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text);font-weight:600;">Tiger ↔ Monkey</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;margin-top:2px;">寅申冲</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:rgba(220,60,60,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(220,60,60,0.18);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:6px;">🐇 ↔ 🐓</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text);font-weight:600;">Rabbit ↔ Rooster</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;margin-top:2px;">卯酉冲</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:rgba(220,60,60,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(220,60,60,0.18);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:6px;">🐉 ↔ 🐕</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text);font-weight:600;">Dragon ↔ Dog</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;margin-top:2px;">辰戌冲</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:rgba(220,60,60,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(220,60,60,0.18);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:6px;">🐍 ↔ 🐗</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text);font-weight:600;">Snake ↔ Pig</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;margin-top:2px;">巳亥冲</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 3: The Six Combinations -->
    <div class="about-section">
      <h3>The Six Combinations (<span style="font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;">六合</span>)</h3>
      <p>The Six Combinations are the most naturally harmonious zodiac pairings. These animals share complementary energies that create mutual support, understanding, and attraction.</p>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:12px;margin-top:16px;">
        <div style="background:rgba(60,180,80,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(60,180,80,0.18);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:6px;">🐀 + 🐂</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text);font-weight:600;">Rat + Ox</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;margin-top:2px;">子丑合</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:rgba(60,180,80,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(60,180,80,0.18);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:6px;">🐅 + 🐗</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text);font-weight:600;">Tiger + Pig</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;margin-top:2px;">寅亥合</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:rgba(60,180,80,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(60,180,80,0.18);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:6px;">🐇 + 🐕</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text);font-weight:600;">Rabbit + Dog</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;margin-top:2px;">卯戌合</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:rgba(60,180,80,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(60,180,80,0.18);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:6px;">🐉 + 🐓</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text);font-weight:600;">Dragon + Rooster</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;margin-top:2px;">辰酉合</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:rgba(60,180,80,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(60,180,80,0.18);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:6px;">🐍 + 🐒</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text);font-weight:600;">Snake + Monkey</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;margin-top:2px;">巳申合</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:rgba(60,180,80,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(60,180,80,0.18);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:6px;">🐎 + 🐑</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text);font-weight:600;">Horse + Goat</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;margin-top:2px;">午未合</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 4: Three Harmony Groups -->
    <div class="about-section">
      <h3>Three Harmony Groups (<span style="font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;">三合</span>)</h3>
      <p>The Three Harmonies are triangular alliances of three zodiac animals that share the same elemental affinity. When all three appear in a relationship or family, they amplify that element's energy.</p>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:12px;margin-top:16px;">
        <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid <%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Fire'] %>33;border-radius:12px;padding:18px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:<%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Fire'] %>;margin-bottom:8px;letter-spacing:0.5px;">FIRE TRIO <span style="font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;">火</span></div>
          <div style="font-size:22px;margin-bottom:6px;">🐅 🐎 🐕</div>
          <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);">Tiger + Horse + Dog</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid <%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Wood'] %>33;border-radius:12px;padding:18px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:<%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Wood'] %>;margin-bottom:8px;letter-spacing:0.5px;">WOOD TRIO <span style="font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;">木</span></div>
          <div style="font-size:22px;margin-bottom:6px;">🐇 🐑 🐗</div>
          <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);">Rabbit + Goat + Pig</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid <%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Metal'] %>33;border-radius:12px;padding:18px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:<%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Metal'] %>;margin-bottom:8px;letter-spacing:0.5px;">METAL TRIO <span style="font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;">金</span></div>
          <div style="font-size:22px;margin-bottom:6px;">🐍 🐓 🐂</div>
          <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);">Snake + Rooster + Ox</div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border:1px solid <%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Water'] %>33;border-radius:12px;padding:18px;text-align:center;">
          <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:<%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Water'] %>;margin-bottom:8px;letter-spacing:0.5px;">WATER TRIO <span style="font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;">水</span></div>
          <div style="font-size:22px;margin-bottom:6px;">🐒 🐀 🐉</div>
          <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);">Monkey + Rat + Dragon</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 5: Types of Compatibility Analysis -->
    <div class="about-section">
      <h3>Types of Compatibility Analysis</h3>
      <p>BaZi compatibility extends beyond romance. The same framework reveals dynamics in any relationship where two charts interact.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:14px;margin-bottom:20px;">
      <div class="about-section" style="text-align:center;padding:24px 16px;">
        <div style="font-size:32px;margin-bottom:8px;">💕</div>
        <h3 style="font-size:15px;margin-bottom:6px;">Romance</h3>
        <p style="font-size:12px;">Element harmony, Day Master compatibility, and emotional resonance between partners. Reveals chemistry, long-term potential, and areas needing conscious effort.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-section" style="text-align:center;padding:24px 16px;">
        <div style="font-size:32px;margin-bottom:8px;">💼</div>
        <h3 style="font-size:15px;margin-bottom:6px;">Business</h3>
        <p style="font-size:12px;">Professional partnerships assessed through complementary strengths, wealth element alignment, and leadership dynamics. Identifies who leads and who supports.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-section" style="text-align:center;padding:24px 16px;">
        <div style="font-size:32px;margin-bottom:8px;">👨‍👩‍👧‍👦</div>
        <h3 style="font-size:15px;margin-bottom:6px;">Family</h3>
        <p style="font-size:12px;">Parent-child and sibling dynamics through generational pillar analysis. Understand nurturing styles, communication gaps, and inherited element patterns.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 6: Element Compatibility -->
    <div class="about-section">
      <h3>Element Compatibility (<span style="font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;">五行相生相克</span>)</h3>
      <p>The Five Elements interact in two fundamental cycles that shape every relationship. Understanding these dynamics reveals the natural energy flow between two people.</p>
      <div style="display:grid;gap:14px;margin-top:16px;">
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;padding:14px;background:rgba(60,180,80,0.04);border-radius:10px;border:1px solid rgba(60,180,80,0.12);">
          <span style="font-size:22px;line-height:1;">🌱</span>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:4px;">Producing Relationship (<span style="font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;">相生</span>)</div>
            <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;">Supportive and nurturing. One partner's element feeds the other:
              <span style="color:<%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Wood'] %>;font-weight:600;">Wood</span> feeds
              <span style="color:<%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Fire'] %>;font-weight:600;">Fire</span> feeds
              <span style="color:<%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Earth'] %>;font-weight:600;">Earth</span> feeds
              <span style="color:<%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Metal'] %>;font-weight:600;">Metal</span> feeds
              <span style="color:<%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Water'] %>;font-weight:600;">Water</span> feeds
              <span style="color:<%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Wood'] %>;font-weight:600;">Wood</span>.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;padding:14px;background:rgba(220,60,60,0.04);border-radius:10px;border:1px solid rgba(220,60,60,0.12);">
          <span style="font-size:22px;line-height:1;">⚔️</span>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:4px;">Controlling Relationship (<span style="font-family:'Noto Sans SC',sans-serif;">相克</span>)</div>
            <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;">Challenging but growth-oriented. One partner's element restrains the other:
              <span style="color:<%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Wood'] %>;font-weight:600;">Wood</span> controls
              <span style="color:<%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Earth'] %>;font-weight:600;">Earth</span>,
              <span style="color:<%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Earth'] %>;font-weight:600;">Earth</span> controls
              <span style="color:<%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Water'] %>;font-weight:600;">Water</span>,
              <span style="color:<%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Water'] %>;font-weight:600;">Water</span> controls
              <span style="color:<%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Fire'] %>;font-weight:600;">Fire</span>,
              <span style="color:<%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Fire'] %>;font-weight:600;">Fire</span> controls
              <span style="color:<%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Metal'] %>;font-weight:600;">Metal</span>,
              <span style="color:<%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Metal'] %>;font-weight:600;">Metal</span> controls
              <span style="color:<%= bazi.EL_COLOR['Wood'] %>;font-weight:600;">Wood</span>.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;padding:14px;background:rgba(240,192,64,0.04);border-radius:10px;border:1px solid rgba(240,192,64,0.12);">
          <span style="font-size:22px;line-height:1;">🤝</span>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:4px;">Same Element</div>
            <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;">Deep understanding and shared wavelength, but potentially competitive. Two people with the same Day Master element may mirror each other's strengths — and blind spots.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 7: Beyond Zodiac Signs -->
    <div class="about-callout">
      <strong>True BaZi compatibility goes far beyond just comparing zodiac animals.</strong> While zodiac clashes and combinations are widely known, they only examine the Year Branch — one of eight characters in a full BaZi chart.
    </div>

    <div class="about-section">
      <h3>Beyond Zodiac Signs</h3>
      <p>A complete compatibility analysis compares all four pillars between two people — Year, Month, Day, and Hour. Each pillar governs different life domains:</p>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:10px;margin:16px 0;">
        <div style="text-align:center;padding:14px 8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border-radius:10px;">
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--gold);font-weight:600;margin-bottom:4px;">YEAR</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);">Social image &amp; family background</div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center;padding:14px 8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border-radius:10px;">
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--gold);font-weight:600;margin-bottom:4px;">MONTH</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);">Career &amp; parents</div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center;padding:14px 8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border-radius:10px;">
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--gold);font-weight:600;margin-bottom:4px;">DAY</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);">Core self &amp; marriage</div>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:center;padding:14px 8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03);border-radius:10px;">
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--gold);font-weight:600;margin-bottom:4px;">HOUR</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);">Inner emotions &amp; children</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>The <strong>Day Master</strong> — the Heavenly Stem of the Day Pillar — is the most important factor in compatibility. It represents your core identity, and its relationship to your partner's Day Master reveals the fundamental dynamic of the partnership.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <div class="about-section">
      <h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
      <div class="about-faq">
        <div class="about-faq-item">
          <div class="about-faq-q">Can BaZi predict if a relationship will work?</div>
          <div class="about-faq-a">BaZi compatibility analysis reveals the natural dynamic between two people — areas of harmony and potential friction. It doesn't predict success or failure, but highlights strengths to nurture and challenges to navigate. A clash doesn't doom a relationship, and a perfect match doesn't guarantee one.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-faq-item">
          <div class="about-faq-q">What if our zodiac signs clash?</div>
          <div class="about-faq-a">A zodiac clash (such as Rat vs Horse) indicates areas of natural tension, but it's only one factor among many. Full BaZi compatibility examines all four pillars, element balance, and Day Master harmony. Many successful relationships have zodiac clashes offset by strong compatibility elsewhere in the chart.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-faq-item">
          <div class="about-faq-q">Is BaZi compatibility the same as zodiac compatibility?</div>
          <div class="about-faq-a">No. Zodiac compatibility only considers the year animal, which is just one of eight characters in a BaZi chart. True BaZi compatibility analyzes both partners' complete Four Pillars — including Day Master, element balance, and all pillar interactions — for a far more nuanced and accurate assessment.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-faq-item">
          <div class="about-faq-q">How important is birth time for compatibility?</div>
          <div class="about-faq-a">Birth time determines the Hour Pillar, which represents inner emotions and private life — crucial for understanding romantic compatibility. Without birth time, you can still assess three of the four pillars, but the Hour Pillar adds significant depth to the analysis, especially for intimate relationships.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="about-cta">
      <a href="/app" class="btn-primary">Explore Your Compatibility →</a>
    </div>
  </main>

  <%- include('../partials/footer') %>

  <script>
    document.querySelectorAll('.about-faq-q').forEach(q => {
      q.addEventListener('click', () => q.closest('.about-faq-item').classList.toggle('open'));
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
